{"tid":242373,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(大埔人入) 係大埔你最鍾意食咩","createTime":"2017-05-14T00:15:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-15T05:36:44.000Z","uid":108894,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ac21d09dbc52e6e308c00c08f2fecafbc5be516e","tid":242373,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T00:15:12.000Z","msg":"各位都知大埔特別係大埔墟一帶係新界東出名多街坊鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大埔墟熟食市場又係多野食揪<br />\n唔知你又鍾意邊間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我就非常鍾意食蔡潤記 (新蔡潤記唔該收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-JqYSa2qZVP8/TzyULE5w8oI/AAAAAAAAH1Y/1x12j_81Eec/s1600/P2164181.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-JqYSa2qZVP8%2FTzyULE5w8oI%2FAAAAAAAAH1Y%2F1x12j_81Eec%2Fs1600%2FP2164181.jpg&h=dcb07d14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n魚蛋河加汁再加碟魚皮一流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (又或者蛋腩河, 因為在下鍾意食牛, 不過其實水準只係中等)<br />\n辣椒油都好夠味, 不過一到中午就比人不到7788<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 幾乎冇渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2388a9af31052d473e2af736446e51f937f96e5","tid":242373,"uid":60245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T00:48:59.000Z","msg":"伙計太串 永不錄用"},{"pid":"53b07921bb1d19be952b117d45439f723f545dda","tid":242373,"uid":113604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T00:49:30.000Z","msg":"紅橋"},{"pid":"e0adbd3888de7b8d26affa29bb6d83f938979180","tid":242373,"uid":28353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T00:50:59.000Z","msg":"欽記"},{"pid":"7cf04342d63d14851fceac5f22659287767bb0c0","tid":242373,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T00:56:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>欽記</blockquote><br />\n欽記都ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係好撚串，唔高興開就唔開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5fbe202db4d2a0967e1805fd2c9212a7bcd99db","tid":242373,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T00:57:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>欽記</blockquote><br />\n而且種類少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be296898ecd6bac2bdb566e9cfd5e497bab3a7f4","tid":242373,"uid":10622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T00:59:32.000Z","msg":"世記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77fa2e2976e6817e72c19218042199ca34f6ba96","tid":242373,"uid":70946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T00:59:51.000Z","msg":"廣福道投注站對面馬路間扒都唔錯<br />\n熟食中心豬扒麵"},{"pid":"c3b17ce46c982b06facadb410aa614db996c1fba","tid":242373,"uid":23703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T01:10:38.000Z","msg":"陳漢記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a65112b0de16fa6d7489149b60d99584d1fbc5d","tid":242373,"uid":56059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T01:11:15.000Z","msg":"食女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c6611c93208131adddd2ac55c2476388b2afcfe","tid":242373,"uid":55870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T01:13:20.000Z","msg":"識食一定食周明園，蔡潤記果啲行開一二邊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ce2aa55b68949e9dc8fd1bcf075363a529d9c79","tid":242373,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T01:14:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>陳漢記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好一般<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家已經幾乎唔食"},{"pid":"32a753b9ef6fd0ef491a7252e5fc988a3c8b34d3","tid":242373,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T01:16:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>識食一定食周明園，蔡潤記果啲行開一二邊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其他唔敢講<br />\n魚蛋粉真係蔡潤記最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cf2edafcfb0022aa44f7ff8125534bc065f716c","tid":242373,"uid":24721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T01:17:17.000Z","msg":"食嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好扺屌"},{"pid":"abb3f4203c8e349763f5d63e7e3674baaf93556a","tid":242373,"uid":34834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T01:19:43.000Z","msg":"miss3 三小姐"},{"pid":"ca131895ac1a01c1c0fb790f3ba26a6239a04e0f","tid":242373,"uid":73823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T01:22:15.000Z","msg":"陳漢記 腸粉真係無得輸 <br />\n萬利車仔麵 佢啲牛丸都好好食<br />\n廣成魚蛋粉 牛筋丸 雲吞係屋企打邊爐必買<br />\n蔡潤記 其實差左但都好食 新蔡潤記就不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大埔街市雪菜雞翼豬扒粗 <br />\n大埔街市李記啲點心都好好食 仲有間賣砵仔糕又係正<br />\n花果山燒賣 以前屋企會買佢啲豉油<br />\n<br />\n住大埔真係無最鐘意食 因為太多好食<br />\n十月返香港準備日日留係大埔<br />\n以加仲要有天仁茗茶 真係唔洗出銅鑼灣旺角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7a075c35cc16c952a06e85b839a666c599ab931","tid":242373,"uid":59762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T01:24:01.000Z","msg":"東興 屋企星期日飯堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bce6b106b6b82c319fa0886bccf31832e925afa","tid":242373,"uid":2774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T01:24:48.000Z","msg":"鴻發牛腩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n民華既茶餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n晚飯小菜就伍仔記"},{"pid":"dd9196c4113925ed5ab70593c9fec23983f7592c","tid":242373,"uid":29497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T01:25:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>欽記</blockquote><br />\n一般<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39f9e4fed6c0ea22ba37a3ca9e22a9754e3435fb","tid":242373,"uid":3586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T01:25:48.000Z","msg":"蔡潤記由細食到大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n細個嗰陣新舊都有食 近幾年新變到好撚難食<br />\n而舊蔡既員工近年既態度都有改善 冇以前咁串"},{"pid":"5b79926d5b7e411c262fa57a80686dcd27f5d080","tid":242373,"uid":1802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T01:29:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>陳漢記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好一般<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家已經幾乎唔食</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢個煲仔飯叫做食得落<br />\n腸粉真的不了，一夾就爛曬，點食"},{"pid":"321361d4fd1ba9f1abd41e21073ef5b0f5d0b34b","tid":242373,"uid":81203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T01:30:30.000Z","msg":"嘉華大排檔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n執左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e79e88c7128a9c9d57867fbfeb590940833ae5c4","tid":242373,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T02:34:16.000Z","msg":"新明發 排骨飯同潮州粉果<br />\n群記清湯腩 完勝中環數字記<img src=\"/assets/face